---
import Layout from '../../layouts/LayoutEn.astro';
---

<Layout title="Foster a pet">
    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-6 text-indigo-800">Become a foster home</h1>
        <p class="text-center text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Opening your home for a while changes a life forever. We cover vet care
            and often food too. We only ask for time, patience, and love.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-10 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">What we provide</h2>
                <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-2">
                    <li>• Ongoing guidance and support.</li>
                    <li>• Vet care and treatments covered by the rescue.</li>
                    <li>• Basic supplies if you need them.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">What we ask</h2>
                <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-2">
                    <li>• A safe space for the first days.</li>
                    <li>• Time for walks and daily care.</li>
                    <li>• Keep us informed of any changes.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-10 bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Foster application</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                We need a few details to start. For example, whether you can isolate the animal
                during the first days and if you have other pets.
            </p>
            <a href="https://tally.so/r/81LjVY" target="_blank" class="bg-indigo-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-indigo-700 transition-colors inline-block">
                Fill out the foster form
            </a>
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>
